- `total_supply_usd`
- `total_borrow_usd`
- `liquidity_usd`
- `utilization`
- `borrow_apy`
- `supply_apy`
- `collateral_apy`
- `collateral_price_usd`
- `loan_price_usd`

`wallet_market_snapshots`

- `snapshot_id`
